- More tests.
- Documentation.
- Ports to other platforms (Windows, MacOS).
- Killer app.
- API bindings for popular programming languages (Java, Python, PHP, C#, Lua).
- Data corruption detection.
- Optimistic concurrency control.

Architecture enhancements:
- Add ybc_item_acquire_de_async() for single-threaded apps.
- Deny ybc_item_acquire_de() call for YBC_SINGLE_THREADED builds.
- Rename ybc_item_acquire* to ybc_item_get*, since other functions also acquire
  items.
- Improve m_storage_allocate() algorithm from O(n*n) to O(n*ln(n)).
